after each sentence

1. *Zabave* su nam uvek bile zanimljive. (Parties were always interesting for us.)
2. Ovi ljudi su bili puni *zabave*. (These people were full of fun.)
3. Nismo imali ništa drugo za *zabavu*. (We didn't have anything else for entertainment.)
4. Ona je iskreno uživala u *zabavi*. (She was genuinely enjoying the party.)
5. Planiramo da napravimo *zabavu*. (We are planning to have a party.)
6. Njegov smeh je bio najveći *zabavu*. (His laugh was the biggest entertainment.)